name: Love what u do
description: 1/1 36mb. I did not purpose the main glitch the piece glitched itself so I left it at edit. If ones loves what they do one would never have to worry, have to fear, have to be ashamed or guilty. Love what u do. But in loving ALL what you do, is true peace. LOVE WHAT YOU DO. Its not just a slogan about a carear. Its a philosophy and a way of life.
